	   <tr><td colspan=2>This is a rather old trick that has been de-bunked by most mages as a very weak substitue to real fighting.&nbsp;&nbsp; Not to mention  the huge experience loss from not doing any dd.<br><br>I always have my Conjure: Elemental spell memorized in case my pet is killed by the mob, but if you don't do any casting, you're wasting alot of precious mana for a very small amount of experience.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
